Requirements
Master server and virtual machines in the cloud of worker instances both use
• Ubuntu 14.04 operating system
• Apache2 server,
• php 5.x,
• python 2.7 and
• python 3.4.
Installing Required Apache2 and PHP5
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install Apache2
sudo apt-get install php5
Installing Required Python Packages for Open Source Tools for
Estonian Natural Language Processing
For extracting named entities, the program uses Open source tools for Estonian natural
language processing (ESTNLTK) [6] package.
By ESTLNK installation guide http://tpetmanson.github.io/estnltk/installation.html, ESTLNK
dependences in Ubuntu Linux 14.04 are:
