Installing ESTNLTK Itself:
sudo apt-get install git
git clone https://github.com/tpetmanson/estnltk estnltk
cd estnltk
python3 setup.py build
sudo python3 setup.py install
python3 -m nltk.downloader punkt
Issue
Hereby a runtime error will be thrown while testing ESTNLTK, because it does not find
the directory named “nltk_data”.
E.g. if its location is under /home/ubuntu, then one must copy it to the place, where
program can find it, one option is /var/www:
cp -a /home/ubuntu/nltk_data /var/www
rm -rf /home/ubuntu/nltk_data
Installing Required Python Packages for Parsing Documents
sudo apt-get install python3-lxml
sudo pip3 install xlrd
sudo pip3 install PyPDF2
Installing required python packages for generating/serializing rdf
files
sudo pip3 install rdflib
Installing Required Python Packages for Using Google API
alias python=python2
pip install --upgrade google-api-python-client
If the pip install is not successful, one can try this command:
sudo easy_install --upgrade google-api-python-client
